ils. The stakes? Sky-high: a poorly constructed model can lead to covenant =
breaches, liquidity crunches, or worse=E2=80=94a complete loss of sponsor e=
quity (and probably your job).</p>



<p>This guide provides a practitioner-focused approach to building robust L=
BO models. Whether you=E2=80=99re an investment banking analyst grinding th=
rough <a href=3D"https://uplevered.com/private-equity-interview-questions/"=
