<p><strong>What =E2=80=98done=E2=80=99 looks like:</strong> Sources =3D Use=
s to the penny. Balance sheet balances every period. Cash flow bridge recon=
ciles to debt paydown. IRR/MOIC move in the right direction when you stress=
