</ol>



<h3 class=3D"wp-block-heading">Balance Sheet</h3>



<ol start=3D"5" class=3D"wp-block-list">
<li>BS balances every period (total assets =3D total liabilities + equity)<=
/li>



<li>Goodwill =3D purchase price =E2=80=93 net tangible assets (simplified) =
or from PPA</li>



<li>Deferred financing fees amortize over debt life</li>



