</ol>



<h3 class=3D"wp-block-heading">Cash Flow</h3>



<ol start=3D"9" class=3D"wp-block-list">
<li>Cash flow bridge: EBITDA =E2=86=92 less taxes =E2=86=92 less capex =E2=
=86=92 less =CE=94NWC =E2=86=92 less interest =E2=86=92 FCF</li>



<li>FCF drives mandatory debt paydown, then sweep, then revolver repayment<=
/li>



