<h3 class=3D"wp-block-heading">Returns</h3>



<ol start=3D"16" class=3D"wp-block-list">
<li>Exit equity =3D exit TEV =E2=80=93 net debt at exit</li>



<li>MOIC =3D exit equity =C3=B7 sponsor equity invested</li>



